data.eml:eml: Deontostoma tridentum n. sp. (Nematoda, Leptosomatidae) from the continental slope of New Zealand

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Leduc, Daniel (2013): Deontostoma tridentum n. sp. (Nematoda, Leptosomatidae) from the continental slope of New Zealand. Zootaxa 3722 (4): 483-492, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3722.4.3
